OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny intervals
OL,6,Fand a few showers, these mainly across
OL,7,Fthe west this morning. Becoming drier
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon. East coast
OL,9,Flargely dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fchilly. Rain will spread from the
OL,13,Fsouthwest for a time overnight. Drier
OL,14,Fweather following on behind later in
OL,15,Fthe night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA dry and mostly cloudy day.
OL,18,FNorthern Moray and northern
OL,19,FAberdeenshire may see some hazy
OL,20,Fsunshine. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
