OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand mild with patchy rain on
OL,7,FWednesday. Bright and breezy with
OL,8,Fscattered showers on Thursday, mainly
OL,9,Fdry in the east. Rain for a time on
OL,10,FFriday.
